{"TopicId":82661,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Very serious Kerbal question.","CreatedByName":"rewdew2","CreatedById":26388,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-24T00:33:25Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"rewdew2","CreatedById":26388,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-24T00:33:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIn \u0027Kerbal Science\u0027 (video linked below) How does the scientists glasses stay on?!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/tu9eoD1ot0A?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Felsmak","CreatedById":27187,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-24T00:36:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThey are strutted to the cranium.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dryer_lint","CreatedById":162541,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-24T01:00:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThey\u0027re attached to him. The \u0022scientists\u0022 are actually just Kerbals that were born with glasses.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rewdew2","CreatedById":26388,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-24T20:27:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWell...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cdn.hark.com/images/000/006/085/6085/original.0\u0022 alt=\u0022original.0\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EVery interesting replies.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"r_rolo1","CreatedById":26192,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-24T20:34:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EVery junior docking ports ? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frank_G","CreatedById":100000,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-24T20:40:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EKerbals have sticky eyeballs... they just smack the glasses on... irgs...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZodiaK","CreatedById":80590,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-24T21:23:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ethe frame stalks are hinged on springs which push them closed. when you pull them open and let go, the snap closed. when one puts them on, they press onto the sides of your heads to stay on. ENGINEERING!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jovus","CreatedById":117163,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-24T21:44:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThis is true for most Kerbal Scientist, but not for Werner von Kerman. His glasses are kept on his face by an extremely miniaturized HEX AI probe body and a suite of carefully tuned RCS thrusters. Thus his pride at being the eminent kerbal scientist - it\u0027s deserved.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FacialJack","CreatedById":114369,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-24T22:10:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ebeware of the explosives glasses !!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dbmorpher","CreatedById":77927,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-25T01:59:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe reason Kraken Drives don\u0027t work now is because the scientists stole them all to keep the glasses pinned to their face.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Razz","CreatedById":119692,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-25T02:41:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Equantum struts!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sirrobert","CreatedById":70591,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-25T14:01:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nikola7007\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Nikola7007\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThey\u0027re attached to him. The \u0022scientists\u0022 are actually just Kerbals that were born with glasses.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EExactly. In much the same way, Kerbalnauts\u0060 spacesuit actually exoskeleton. Those that have such an exoskeleton become kerbalnauts\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}